Hello,

Our limelight is on the fritz… I connected to the limelight direct via a USB to ethernet adapter, went to limelight.local:5801, and saw the dashboard. Problem: The camera stream cannot be accessed at 5800!

This is probably some sort of Network error, we are using a static IP, however our roborio is default IP configuration, but this all shouldn’t matter if we are directly ethernet connected to the limelight.

We tried two computers, browsers, and refreshed and used different IP configurations.

I am pretty sure it will work with the radio wireless, but at comps so will test tommorow.

TLDR: Connect to limelight direct via ethernet, cannot access :5800 for stream, but :5801 for dashboard works.
